					<a class="aui-arrow-right">网络状态</a>
				</li>
				<li class="aui-list-view-cell" onclick="shake();">
					<a class="aui-arrow-right">点击之后摇一摇</a>
				</li>
				<li class="aui-list-view-cell" onclick="right_cle();">
					<a class="aui-arrow-right">点击之后向右滑动页面试试看</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="aui-content aui-card">
			<ul class="aui-list-view">
				<li class="aui-list-view-cell" onclick="appinfo();">
					<a class="aui-arrow-right">应用和设备信息</a>
				</li>
				<li class="aui-list-view-cell" onclick="contack();">
					<a class="aui-arrow-right">点击获取您的联系人信息并上传</a>
				</li>
				<li class="aui-list-view-cell" onclick="openContacks();">
					<a class="aui-arrow-right">回到首页</a>
